fragment_downloaded_cb({"url": "Reference-manual.html#get_option", "fragment": "get_option \nObtains the value of the project build option specified in the positional argument. \nNote that the value returned for built in options that end in dir such as bindir and libdir is always a path relative to and inside the prefix. \nThe only exceptions are sysconfdir localstatedir and sharedstatedir which will return the value passed during configuration as is which may be absolute or relative to prefix. install_dir arguments handles that as expected but if you need the absolute path to one of these e.g. to use in a define etc. you should use join_paths get_option prefix get_option localstatedir \nFor options of type feature a special object is returned instead of a string. See feature options documentation for more details. \n"});